{"type": "article", "id": 12624, "title": "切西瓜刀", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-27T07:06:42Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 57, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702154218Q0DISTX3bljNYqBG.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t没有西瓜的夏天怎么能叫夏天呢，而人们在切西瓜上的追求也从没间断过。这是一个由奇妙商品供应商 Monkey Business 推出的切西瓜“神器”，上部是塑料，下部是不锈钢，像是一个饼干塑形器，把 “Pepo” 用力按在西瓜上，就可以切出可爱的形状。这是<a href=\"http://www.mnkbusiness.com/?___store=en\" target=\"_blank\">Monkey Business 的官方网站</a>，点击可以购买 “Pepo” ，也可以查看他们更多作品。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140327HiamzxOSRpPA5CrD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.95721271\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140328dDWjGKQeMt4YfPZ2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.04645477\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140328b2dkN0Ds3CKFX1ta.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.59413203\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261403298NL2QFo9EBfXquPg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5794621\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140329NPLMrVFsf1XAk7JH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.81784841\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140330GWDsPIMYj4N3qREJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.93520782\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}